author: Bethesda Softworks
description:
The Writhing Wall has fallen, and the Stirk Fellowship marches eastward. It's time to strike at the heart of the Worm Cult and defeat them once and for all!! Discover a new region twisted and warped by fragments of Coldharbour as you explore Eastern Solstice.

Seasons of the Worm Cult Part 2 is now live on PC/Mac and both Xbox and PlayStation consoles. Eastern Solstice unlocks once the Writhing Wall Event has completed for your server.
